text: Pat McCarthy is an American politician from the state of Washington. She is the Washington State Auditor. McCarthy previously served as school board director for the Tacoma School District (1987–1999)Pat McCarthy - Ballotpedia Retrieved 2018-12-16. and as the County Executive for Pierce County, Washington. == Personal life == Her husband, John, has served on the Port of Tacoma commission and as a judge of the Pierce County Superior Court.
